data.description: Welcome to Playa del Sol! This stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom condo with its spacious layout and modern design offers a comfortable and stylish living. Step inside and be greeted by an abundance of natural light that fills the open-concept living and dining area. With a size of 1,777 square feet, there is no shortage of space in this condo. The bedrooms in this condo are generously sized, providing plenty of room for relaxation and personalization. This property also offers the convenience of two parking spaces, ensuring that you never have to worry about finding a spot for your vehicles. Whether you're looking to entertain guests or simply enjoy some downtime, you'll find plenty of room to spread out and make this place your own. Located in a desirable neighborhood, this condo is surrounded by amenities such as shopping centers, restaurants, parks, and schools. Commuting is a breeze with easy access to major highways and public transportation options, within 10 Miles from Otay Ranch Shopping Center and 5 miles from CBX. The community is known for its peaceful ambiance and friendly neighbors, making it an ideal place to call home. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this incredible condo! Whether you're a first-time buyer or looking to upgrade your current living situation, this property has everything you need. Schedule a viewing today and discover the perfect blend of style, comfort, and convenience that awaits you!
